data.description: : **MOTIVATED SELLER!!** Seller has found a new home and ready to move! Call today to book your time to view this home and bring an offer! *** Absolutely beautiful ranch home just outside city limits and in a nice subdivision. This house offers great space for the family. With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths at one end of the home and a bonus room and full bath at the other end of the house, you can have so much privacy. This gorgeous home is located right outside of city limits but just five minutes from shopping. Located at the lower end of a beautiful subdivision with mild restrictions and no HOA. Step inside to a spacious livingroom and kitchen/dining room. This home has two master suites on separate ends of the home. The bonus room is being used as a master bedroom with a master bath and jet tub. Off of the living room is the two bedrooms, full bath and other master bedroom and full bath. Move from the dining room outside onto a back deck that opens up to the pool area. This beautiful inground pool is completely fenced and perfect for those backyard BBQ's and family gatherings. Two car garage in back also offers lots of storage space. This is a must-see property! Call today to schedule your time to view this beautiful home!
